            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>de</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> Minervae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>urelius</ex></expan> Iustius <lb n="3"/>Belatullus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>mag</abbr><ex>ister</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>plum</abbr><ex cert="low">ariorum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Aspro et Aspro </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> c<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>o</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona, Z. 8 auf der crepido. Z. 5: möglicherweise auch plum(bariorum). (B): Herz; Selzer: AE 1976: Z. 1: [in]; Herz; AE 1976:Z. 5: plu[m(ariorum)]; Selzer: Z. 5: plu(mariorum); Z. 8: c(on)s(ulibus).</p>
            </div>
